{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_BoPvyiqKPKfjf7OlmLZzkhnU","type":"tool_result","content":"{\"type\":\"Stack\",\"props\":{\"gap\":2},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"Heading\",\"props\":{\"level\":2},\"children\":[\"Here's what you've got — it's actually a great set\"]},{\"type\":\"Paragraph\",\"props\":{},\"children\":[\"Between your notes, spreadsheet, the park-fee PDF, the photo, and your voice memo, you've actually captured the whole trip. It's just scattered — which is exactly what you said. Here's the inventory:\"]},{\"type\":\"Card\",\"props\":{\"title\":\"📝 tanzaniamemories.md\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"Paragraph\",\"props\":{},\"children\":[\"Your running trip notes — key stops, practical tips, things to remember, and a few to-dos. Covers the route, the safari operator details (Richard at the office), and assorted advice you've collected.\"]}]},{\"type\":\"Card\",\"props\":{\"title\":\"💰 trip-costs.xlsx\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"Paragraph\",\"props\":{},\"children\":[\"Your cost tracker spreadsheet — every expense broken down by category with amounts and notes. This has the real numbers: flights, safari balance, accommodation, tips, the works.\"]}]},{\"type\":\"Card\",\"props\":{\"title\":\"🏞️ ngorongoro-conservation-area-tariffs.pdf\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"Paragraph\",\"props\":{},\"children\":[\"The official Ngorongoro Conservation Area fee schedule — entry fees, camping fees, vehicle fees, and crucially the validity dates so you know what applies when you're there.\"]}]},{\"type\":\"Card\",\"props\":{\"title\":\"📸 stone-town-zanzibar.jpg\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"Paragraph\",\"props\":{},\"children\":[\"A courtyard shot looking up at one of those classic Stone Town buildings — whitewashed walls, arched windows with wooden shutters, carved dark-wood balconies stacked up. It's your Zanzibar anchor photo.\"]}]},{\"type\":\"Card\",\"props\":{\"title\":\"🎙️ Voice memo — Ngorongoro crater day\"},\"children\":[{\"typ